  "body": "We have multiple services that are in part parameterized by the user's risk tolerance for reorgs.\r\n\r\n`pruning-blocks-retained` and `Xsynchronizer-fast-sync-pivot-distance` for example.\r\n\r\nI propose we create a new flag that will create a floor for these parameters, ensuring that those services are at least as wary of chain reorgs as the user would like them to be.",
